{"tid":2062254,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"讀Engine Science Design嘅入一入黎，香港好需要你地","createTime":"2020-06-13T04:20:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T14:53:30.000Z","uid":325377,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"166210cbe1ca6a36113b7631a1077b7048b8842e","tid":2062254,"uid":325377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:20:30.000Z","msg":"香港相關學科排名咁高，出到黎個個轉哂行，為咩？<br />\n<br />\n你讀嘅野對世界好有用，諗下apple, dyson, tesla出新product大家幾興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去大公司打份牛工賣肝，老闆賺到笑。如果對份工無興趣，幾十年後除咗層樓，你仲得到d咩？<br />\n<br />\n你夢想中嘅世界係點？呢個時代講disruption, 你做嘅野可以取代舊市場嘅價值，成個market就係你。 FAANG founders發達嗰陣, ibanker只可以做跟尾狗撈下油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe world is your oyster! 買部3d printer，開個github，放idea上Kickstarter，你嘅人生旅途岩岩先開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aba67176d745d1a987de3c0a3248eca342c3bce","tid":2062254,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"因為香港嗰啲僵化嘅課程根本同世界脫節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb4896490ba155ff19033fb9a664b7d6fa36b68","tid":2062254,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:36:03.000Z","msg":"kickstarter大把<br />\n咖啡機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有香港特色嘅新創企業<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95889ba42b930cd17a2613778990eabc4be0f6e1","tid":2062254,"uid":43008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:40:36.000Z","msg":"你地唔係好鐘意踩呢3類人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad944d004c721ca3c653dabf6ef3d40124d8c8b","tid":2062254,"uid":66049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T04:45:00.000Z","msg":"創新創條毛咩<br />\n政府PR政治show<br />\n咪又係抄<br />\n創業成本又高<br />\n香港地唔使生活？<br />\n夢想搵到飯食？<br />